    "description": "Starsiege: Deadzone is a multiplayer corridor extraction shooter set in a dark sci-fi universe where humanity is on the brink of extinction. As space mercenaries, known as Raiders, players will team up with two others to explore the derelict stations taken over by sentient AI. As a Raider, your goal is to extract valuable weapons and resources for your faction. Players will prepare themselves before venturing into procedurally generated ships; making each match unique. Customize your loadout and select from many abilities and perks providing your own unique playstyle. Work alone or together to overcome the ship's deadly traps, defenses, and other Raiders in order to escape.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Tactical PVP Combat:</strong> Use a variety of discovered weapons and equipment to take out other Raiders and survive each mission. Select &amp; customize your loadouts to best suit you and your team.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170420/extras/f3353f995837afa8826c6f3e9b20ae76.poster.avif?t=1707929269\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170420/extras/f3353f995837afa8826c6f3e9b20ae76.webm?t=1707929269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170420/extras/f3353f995837afa8826c6f3e9b20ae76.mp4?t=1707929269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> <strong>Procedurally Generated Ships:</strong> Each mission is a unique experience with a different layout to explore. The space stations are filled with deadly traps, defenses, and rival Raiders.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170420/extras/c7c5de354a318480846214d95e168eac.poster.avif?t=1707929269\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170420/extras/c7c5de354a318480846214d95e168eac.webm?t=1707929269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170420/extras/c7c5de354a318480846214d95e168eac.mp4?t=1707929269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> <strong>Hardcore Gameplay:</strong> Face a variety of dangerous enemies in each room, and be ready to retreat and find another path if necessary. With limited respawns every decision matters.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170420/extras/743a5cf3a33611f23eea00edb5913c2e.poster.avif?t=1707929269\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170420/extras/743a5cf3a33611f23eea00edb5913c2e.webm?t=1707929269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170420/extras/743a5cf3a33611f23eea00edb5913c2e.mp4?t=1707929269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> <strong>Dynamic Light &amp; Darkness:</strong> Shoot out lights to create darkness and ambush enemies. Use your flashlight to prospect the ship’s darkest corners. The use of light and darkness is critical to your success or demise in The Deadzone.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170420/extras/e515639e309d78e901b5c2a8a5cf6563.poster.avif?t=1707929269\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170420/extras/e515639e309d78e901b5c2a8a5cf6563.webm?t=1707929269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170420/extras/e515639e309d78e901b5c2a8a5cf6563.mp4?t=1707929269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> <strong>High-Stakes Extraction:</strong> The ship is crumbling and time is running out. Find valuable resources and escape pods before it's too late, but beware - there are only enough escape pods for half of the players in each match. If you don't make it out, you'll lose everything.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170420/extras/5f6a2664d441e34c3080c40dacc84c6a.poster.avif?t=1707929269\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170420/extras/5f6a2664d441e34c3080c40dacc84c6a.webm?t=1707929269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170420/extras/5f6a2664d441e34c3080c40dacc84c6a.mp4?t=1707929269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
